# CAT-ROUTER env example
#
# Default: synthetic catalog at data/model_catalog.json. No env vars required.
#
# To swap to a live Kamiwaza Model Gateway:
KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL=https://kamiwaza.local/api/v1
KAMIWAZA_API_KEY=replace-with-your-jwt-or-static-token
#
# (The shared LLM client at shared/kamiwaza_client.py auto-detects whichever
# of KAMIWAZA / OPENROUTER / OPENAI / ANTHROPIC is set — see DEPLOY.md.)
